    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You draw your weapon in a circular motion to freeze your enemy before slashing again to shatter the ice.</em><br />  Make two melee Taijutsu attacks dealing your weapons damage. On each hit, the target must also succeed a Constitution saving throw, gaining 1 rank of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em> on a failed save.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a <em><strong>Chain 1</strong></em>, you gain a +1 bonus to your next attack roll.<br />  If this jutsu is cast as a <em><strong>Chain 2</strong></em>, make an additional melee Taijutsu attack which also knocks the creature back 15 feet on a failed Constitution saving throw, instead of gaining an additional rank of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em>.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the target suffers a -1 penalty on their save.</p>",
